RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Snohomish city, WA operates under a strong mayor-council government. The City Council members are elected at-large, so there are no specific wards or districts beyond their position numbers. Terms for Mayor Redmon and Council Members Merrill, Flynn, Burke, and Guzak end December 31, 2025. Terms for Council Members Hetherington, Kuleta, and Neals end December 31, 2027.
